data.description: COME SEE this beautiful home located in THE GRAND community. Full 3-bedrooms,with a den that makes a great office , Plantation Shutters throughout the home. Gas Fireplace in Great Room, Beautiful GOURMENT kitchen  Granite Countertops, Lots of Cabinets and Storage! Laundry Room includes  Washer/Dryer w/drawers, Utility Sink & Cabinets.  Massive Bay Windows that offers an unobstructed view of the Entertainer's Backyard with a waterfall, Built-in BBQ Grill, Extended Patio Cover, Gas Firepit, Beautiful mature landscaping, Large Garage with lots of storage and cabinets. Home has water softer and solar panels. This home has pride of ownership and is a must see!!!
